OL,3,CJob vacancies across UK fall to lowest
OL,4,Clevel in five years
OL,6,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,7,F(ONS) said vacancies in the UK have
OL,8,Ffallen to their lowest level for five
OL,9,Fyears, with a significant drop seen
OL,10,Facross retail and hospitality sectors
OL,11,Fand smaller employers.
OL,13,FThe largest fall in the quarter was in
OL,14,Fprofessional services.
OL,16,FJob vacancies fell by 19,000 to
OL,17,F707,000 in the three months to May -
OL,18,Fthe lowest level since the three
OL,19,Fmonths to April 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
