OL,3,CJob vacancies across UK fall to lowest
OL,4,Clevel in five years
OL,6,FHowever, the latest figures also show
OL,7,FBritain's rate of unemployment edged
OL,8,Flower to 4.9% in the three months to
OL,9,FApril, down from 5% in the three
OL,10,Fmonths to March.
OL,12,FThe data comes before the Bank of
OL,13,FEngland is set to announce its
OL,14,Finterest rate decision at noon on
OL,15,FThursday, with experts expecting rates
OL,16,Fto hold at 3.75%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
