OL,3,CJob vacancies across UK fall to lowest
OL,4,Clevel in five years
OL,6,FWage growth, meanwhile, remained
OL,7,Funchanged at 3.4% in the three months
OL,8,Fto April after recently easing back,
OL,9,Fand continues to outstrip inflation,
OL,10,Frising by 0.3% after taking Consumer
OL,11,FPrices Index inflation into account.
OL,13,FLiz McKeown, ONS director of economic
OL,14,Fstatistics, said there were "some
OL,15,Fsigns of workers moving into
OL,16,Fselfemployment", while the vacancies
OL,17,Fdecline signalled firms are "becoming
OL,18,Fmore cautious about taking on new
OL,19,Fstaff".
