OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781830076
OL,3,CJob vacancies across UK fall to lowest
OL,4,Clevel in five years
OL,6,FThe ONS said its vacancies survey
OL,7,Fshowed some firms are putting
OL,8,Frecruitment on hold due to economic
OL,9,Funcertainty and higher labour costs.
OL,11,FThe government hiked employee National
OL,12,FInsurance Contributions in April last
OL,13,Fyear, while firms have also been hit
OL,14,Fby above-inflation rises in the
OL,15,Fminimum wage.
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
