PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781830076
OL,3,CJob vacancies across UK fall to lowest
OL,4,Clevel in five years
OL,6,FEmployee-heavy sectors such as retail
OL,7,Fand hospitality have been knocked
OL,8,Fparticularly hard by the changes.
OL,10,FThe ONS said on an annual basis, the
OL,11,Fwholesale and retail trade sector saw
OL,12,Fthe largest fall in vacancies, down
OL,13,F13,000 in the three months to May,
OL,14,Fwhile hospitality recorded a 10,000
OL,15,Fdrop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
