OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781830076
OL,3,CJob vacancies across UK fall to lowest
OL,4,Clevel in five years
OL,6,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,7,FMcFadden has blamed the economic shock
OL,8,Ffrom the war in Iran for the decline,
OL,9,F"this month's figures show that there
OL,10,Fare 400,000 more people in work than
OL,11,Fthis time last year, but we know
OL,12,Fongoing instability in the Middle East
OL,13,Fis causing uncertainty in our labour
OL,14,Fmarket".
OL,16,F"We have the right economic plan for
OL,17,Fgrowth and stability in a volatile
OL,18,Fworld - and we are taking action to
OL,19,Fcreate opportunity and make sure that
OL,20,Fno one is left behind," he said.
